| **4: Deployment** | 4 months | 도구화 | IDE plugin + paper |

### **3.2 핵심 알고리즘 3가지**

**Algorithm 1: Tensor Semantics Extraction**
- MatMul: `∀i,j,k: C[i,j] := A[i,k] × B[k,j] + C[i,j]`
- Conv2D: `∀n,h,w,c: O[n,h,w,c] := ∑(I[n,h+kh,w+kw,kc] × K[kh,kw,kc,c])`
- Add: `∀i,j: C[i,j] := A[i,j] + B[i,j]`

**Algorithm 2: SMT Encoding (Z3)**
```smt2
(declare-const A (Array Int Int Real))
(declare-const B (Array Int Int Real))
(declare-const C (Array Int Int Real))

; Verify: Original MatMul ≡ Tiled MatMul
(assert (forall ((i Int) (j Int))
  (= (original-matmul i j)
     (tiled-matmul (div i 64) (div j 64)))))

(check-sat)  ; Should return "unsat" (sound)
```

**Algorithm 3: Incremental Proof Cache**
- Cache key generation
- SMT solver call (100ms - 10s)
- Proof caching (1-10ms lookup)
- Counterexample generation

### **3.3 예상 성능**

```
Micro-benchmarks:
  MatMul 2K×2K verification:   ~500ms
  Conv2D verification:          ~800ms
  Loop Fusion verification:     ~200ms

Cached lookups:
  Average time:                 <10ms
  Cache hit rate:               70-85% (expected)

Real-world models:
  ResNet-50 verification:       ~30 seconds
  BERT-Base verification:       ~15 seconds
  GPT-2 verification:           ~20 seconds
```

